++ Application Portalling

AP is the awareness of [Applications] installed on TheSystem through [Portalling].

This is accomplished through:
    * InternalConfiguration
    * ExternalConfiguration
    * [Zones]
    * ApplicationManagement
    * ComponentryConfiguration

++Architecture

The [CapabilityStore] for uninstalled and installed can rendered as a StateList in the form of a table. This will display properties such as:
    * web based

ComprehensiveSystem and IndepthData mean that extensive information is available regarding applications. To present this data in a meaningful fashion, portalling is used to make it easy readable.

